                <h1>Convicted jihadist, former Guantanamo Bay interrogator talk religious extremism </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/f9cd3f55-e6c6-4f45-93f9-0395db85f179.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

